===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|sir|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|sire||master, sir, lord|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|senior||[[older]], [[elder]]|lang=la}}, from {{term|senex||old|lang=la}}. Compare [[sire]], [[signor]], [[seignior]], [[señor]].

